{"word":"Seed","slug":"seed","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Seed</b> Every herb, tree, and grass, yields its own<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=12'>Gen 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=1&verse=29'>Gen 1:29</a><br/> Each kind has its own body<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=38'>1Co 15:38</a><br/> Not to be mingled in sowing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=19'>Lev 19:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=9'>Deu 22:9</a><br/> Parables concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13'>Mat 13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8'>Luk 8</a><br/> Illustrative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=11&verse=6'>Ecc 11:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=10&verse=12'>Hos 10:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=9&verse=6'>2Co 9:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=6&verse=8'>Gal 6:8</a><br/> Sowing of, type of burial of the body<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=38'>1Co 15:38</a>"}]}